Purpose

The purpose of this independent analysis is to analyze plot synopses of movies. For this analysis, I have used the dataset that was published in LREC 2018 @Miyazaki, Japan. The dataset includes 14K plot synopses from imdb and wikipedia. However, I have only used a subset of it to provide a deep understanding.

In this analysis, I tried to follow a similar methodology with the Kar et al.(2018) study. They also used the same dataset to analyze taggig of each movie. If you are interested in their work, you can find the article here.

Guiding Question

In this analysis, I address the following question: What are the topics that indicated in movies written plot synopsis?

Preparing the Dataset

The dataset includes 14K movie plot synopses and 70 tags. To clearly apply the LDA and STM packages, I created a subset (n=50) and removed the tags.
